  <brief_title>Nilotinib Pharmacokinetics (PK) in Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumor (GIST)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pharmacokinetic Study of Nilotinib in Patients With Metastatic or Unresectable Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumor Showing Failure to Both Imatinib and Sunitinib</official_title>
