  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In patients who are receiving nilotinib, nilotinib plasma levels will be measured after 1
      month of nilotinib treatment. The relationship between surgery type and nilotinib
      pharmakokinetic properties will be investigated in this study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
